        ConfigMaskDummy0,
        ConfigMarketTypeIsStrikedMask, // = 1
        ConfigMaskDummy2,
        ConfigMaskDummy3,
        ConfigIntervalTypeIsUsedMask // = 4
    }

    enum SettlementType {
        FINAL, // = 0
        PRELIMINARY_FIRST // = 1
        //PRELIMINARY_MAX // = 65535
    }

    enum MarketInterval {
        NONE, // = 0

        WEEKLY, // = 4
        DAILY, // = 5
        HOURLY, // = 6
